short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Prevents you from muting your microphone on Google Meet

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The extension automatically unmutes your Google Meet if you attempt to mute it.

P.S This is a fun extension and is not meant for any serious use case.
